SIMPLE: indefinitely
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Indefinitely
<hw>In*def"i*nite*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an indefinite manner
or degree; without any settled limitation; vaguely; not with certainty
or exactness; <as>as, to use a word
<ex>indefinitely</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>If the world be <qex>indefinitely</qex> extended, that is, so far
as no human intellect can fancy any bound of it.</q>
<rj><qau>Ray.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Indefiniteness</ent>⟦br⟧
